The provided `anim` pointer is not valid once this call returns.

@param anim AnimationBase to dispose of.

@since This function is available since SDL_image 3.0.0.

@sa AnimationBase.AnimationBase
@sa AnimationBase.AnimationBase
@sa AnimationBase.AnimationBase

Animation.doc:
